Package se.arkalix.dto.json

Interface JsonWritable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DtoWritable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JsonCollection, JsonValue
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonArray, JsonBoolean, JsonNull, JsonNumber, JsonObject, JsonString
    public interface JsonWritable
extends DtoWritable
    Represents a type that can be written as JSON.

    Do not implement this interface directly. It is implemented automatically by generated DTO classes where JSON is specified as a writable encoding.

    See Also:
    RFC 8259
